        <page n="02" image="va.au.ss.1864.02.23.02">
            <div type="a">
                <column>1</column>
                <head>A Trio of Important Bills</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt>"The new legislation depends for its success upon its prompt, energetic,
                    zealous execution. It requires to be administered by a corps of men in good
                    earnest about their work, fully impressed with its vital importance, and
                    strongly actuated by a sense of individual responsibility."</excerpt>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Urges readers to save the copy of this week's Spectator so that they will
                    know exactly what is contained in the military, tax and currency bills.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
