            <div type="a">
                <column>6</column>
                <head>Our Prospects</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt>"We were never more confident ourselves, and have an abiding faith that the
                    great body of the people will exert their energies to sustain the country and
                    its cause, the war will end in a blaze of glory for the South ere the frosts of
                    another winter shall fall upon us."</excerpt>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Praises the cheerfulness with which the people have responded to the recent
                    tax, military, and currency bills.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
